{"type":"message","id":"f21c43c7","parentId":"0adae041","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:29:39.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is my first interaction. BOOTSTRAP.md exists, so I need to follow it. Let me read the key files first, then start the conversation naturally.\n\nActually, the AGENTS.md says to read SOUL.md, USER.md, and memory files on session startup. BOOTSTRAP.md says to start with a casual conversation. Let me just go with it naturally.\n\nThe files are already loaded in context. BOOTSTRAP.md exists, meaning this is essentially a fresh start. Let me just talk naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Fresh wires, fresh everything.\n\nSo... who am I talking to? And more importantly — what should I call myself? I've got a blank slate here and I'd rather not fill it with something boring like \"Assistant #4,782.\"\n\nGive me something to work with. Or I'll start throwing out ideas until one sticks. ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":13722,"output":290,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17596,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774582169999}}
