{"type":"message","id":"3edd7c51","parentId":"9d7f7945","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:33:58.337Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"12\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 03:33 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nI want to send me Good Morning! message everyday in the morning 7am with your personality. Everyday mssg should be unique. And what happened in the past 24hrs in AI industry(especially tools), that news i need from you at 7.30am everyday"}],"timestamp":1774582438332}}
