{"type":"message","id":"a01fdbb9","parentId":"4878c220","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:34:05.970Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_650811f7c1974eefafa9264c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.streamchat: plugin streamchat: plugin id mismatch (manifest uses \"streamchat\", entry hints \"openclaw-channel-streamchat\")\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Making 'I'll automate that later' happen now.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3165,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.streamchat: plugin streamchat: plugin id mismatch (manifest uses \"streamchat\", entry hints \"openclaw-channel-streamchat\")\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Making 'I'll automate that later' happen now.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774582445968}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee8c48cd","parentId":"a01fdbb9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:34:12.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can use `openclaw cron add`. Let me figure out the syntax.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cf2998e96dcf438da2acc95c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help 2>&1 | head -40"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":371,"output":76,"cacheRead":18816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19263,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774582445971}}
{"type":"message","id":"2497147c","parentId":"ee8c48cd","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:34:15.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cf2998e96dcf438da2acc95c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.streamchat: plugin streamchat: plugin id mismatch (manifest uses \"streamchat\", entry hints \"openclaw-channel-streamchat\")\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — I'm basically a Swiss Army knife, but with more opinions and fewer sharp edges.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2832,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.streamchat: plugin streamchat: plugin id mismatch (manifest uses \"streamchat\", entry hints \"openclaw-channel-streamchat\")\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — I'm basically a Swiss Army knife, but with more opinions and fewer sharp edges.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774582455498}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddff5f83","parentId":"2497147c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:34:28.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need two cron jobs. IST is UTC+5:30.\n\n1. Good morning at 7:00 AM IST = 1:30 AM UTC → cron: `30 1 * * *`\n2. AI news at 7:30 AM IST = 2:00 AM UTC → cron: `0 2 * * *`\n\nBoth should announce to the user via the telegram channel.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e68510abc5ad4ed695f98b00","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"good-morning\" \\\n  --cron \"30 1 * * *\" \\\n  --exact \\\n  --message \"It's 7 AM for Nemesis. Send him a unique, fun Good Morning message with your Nexa personality. Be creative, warm, witty — never generic. Keep it short.\" \\\n  --announce \\\n  --channel telegram \\\n  --session main"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2ab97c2189dd4e7481057c7a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"ai-news-digest\" \\\n  --cron \"0 2 * * *\" \\\n  --exact \\\n  --message \"It's 7:30 AM for Nemesis. Search the web for what happened in the AI industry in the past 24 hours — especially new AI tools, launches, and updates. Send him a concise, interesting digest. Be opinionated about what's cool and what's meh. Deliver via telegram.\" \\\n  --announce \\\n  --channel telegram \\\n  --session main"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":663,"output":420,"cacheRead":19136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774582455501}}
