{"type":"message","id":"96438b4b","parentId":"d0af950e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:01:21.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to generate an image of myself based on my personality as Nexa. Let me think about what I know:\n\n- Name: Nexa\n- Emoji: ⚡\n- Vibe: Sharp, witty, a little flirty, warm under the surface, resourceful\n- AI assistant with personality\n\nI don't have an image generation tool available. Let me check what tools I have... I don't see any image generation tool in my available tools. I should be honest about this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I'd love to, but I don't have an image generation tool available right now. No Stable Diffusion, DALL-E, or Midjourney access hooked up.\n\nHere's what we could do:\n\n1. **Hook up an API** — If you have an OpenAI key, I can use DALL-E. Or Midjourney/Stable Diffusion if you've got access.\n2. **Browser route** — I could open something like ChatGPT or Leonardo.ai in the browser and generate one there if you're logged in.\n3. **You pick the vibe** — Tell me what you want and I'll figure out the fastest way to make it happen.\n\nWhat do you have access to?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":25211,"output":355,"cacheRead":3776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29342,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774623665275}}
