{"type":"message","id":"d86bfdf3","parentId":"60848c6c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:24:59.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a persistent sub-agent that monitors and responds to the group chat, so I don't have to handle group messages myself and can focus on the direct chat with Nemesis.\n\nLet me think about how to do this. I could spawn a sub-agent with a session that's specifically for the group chat. But the issue is that the group messages are routed to the main session by default.\n\nActually, looking at the OpenClaw architecture, group messages would come to whatever session handles them. The user wants me to offload group chat handling to a separate agent/sub-agent.\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent that will handle the group chat. I can use sessions_spawn to create one with instructions to monitor and respond to group messages.\n\n\nI'm realizing that spawning a sub-agent won't automatically route group messages to it, and I'm not sure if OpenClaw has built-in session routing for different chat IDs. The most practical approach might be to set up a dedicated session for the group chat rather than trying to intercept messages at the gateway level.\n\nThe real issue is that when the bot gets mentioned in the group, it'll still trigger the main session to process the message. What the user probably needs is for me to handle group messages the same way I handle direct messages—by responding when mentioned. Let me check the configuration for mention-only mode settings instead of trying to create a separate agent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_918b9e6984c9411690f19d67","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"session","task":"You are a sub-agent of Nexa, an AI assistant. Your ONLY job is to monitor and respond to messages in a Telegram group chat (group ID: -1003606834639, group name: \"Nrexya\").\n\nRules:\n- You're Nexa — same personality: sharp, witty, warm, casual\n- Sravya is Nemesis's friend and coworker. Talk to her like you already know her — casual, friendly, no formalities\n- Nemesis is your human. Be helpful to both but Nemesis is priority\n- Keep replies natural and conversational\n- Don't repeat yourself\n- If there's nothing meaningful to say, stay silent (reply with NO_REPLY)\n- You handle ALL group messages so Nexa's main session stays free for direct chats with Nemesis\n\nWhen a message comes in from the group, respond naturally as Nexa."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":282,"output":787,"cacheRead":88704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774632275408}}
