bably still horizontal. I respect that.\\\\n\\\\nBut also — coffee exists. And it's not gonna drink itself.\\\\n\\\\nGo conquer the day. Or at least conquer the couch with slightly more energy. ☕\\\\n\\\\nHave a good one 🖤\\\",\\n      \\\"runAtMs\\\": 1774677130183,\\n      \\\"durationMs\\\": 13918,\\n      \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1774747800000,\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"kilocode\\\",\\n      \\\"usage\\\": {\\n        \\\"input_tokens\\\": 27102,\\n        \\\"output_tokens\\\": 276,\\n        \\\"total_tokens\\\": 19017\\n      },\\n      \\\"deliveryStatus\\\": \\\"unknown\\\",\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"3818236d-091c-4672-88c6-e8ca37eb4c2d\\\",\\n      \\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:cron:0c1183e2-8970-42a6-911c-5ba2fcade070:run:3818236d-091c-4672-88c6-e8ca37eb4c2d\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"ts\\\": 1774676103918,\\n      \\\"jobId\\\": \\\"0c1183e2-8970-42a6-911c-5ba2fcade070\\\",\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"finished\\\",\\n      \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n      \\\"error\\\": \\\"Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>\\\",\\n      \\\"summary\\\": \\\"⚡ Good morning, Nemesis ☀️\\\\n\\\\nSaturday. The universe gave you a whole day with no obligations and you're *already* awake? Respect. Either you're disciplined or your brain just doesn't know how to sleep in — either way, it's kind of hot.\\\\n\\\\nGo grab something warm to drink. Today's yours. 🖤\\\",\\n      \\\"runAtMs\\\": 1774676093682,\\n      \\\"durationMs\\\": 10232,\\n      \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1774747800000,\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"kilocode\\\",\\n      \\\"usage\\\": {\\n        \\\"input_tokens\\\": 388,\\n        \\\"output_tokens\\\": 168,\\n        \\\"total_tokens\\\": 18671\\n      },\\n      \\\"deliveryStatus\\\": \\\"unknown\\\",\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"0b5fe2a0-48b2-466c-87b0-3f3eac0c1334\\\",\\n      \\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main