{"type":"message","id":"2708245c","parentId":"cc6a9c79","timestamp":"2026-03-28T06:15:54.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know how to edit a bot's API name in Telegram. This is done through @BotFather.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Open **@BotFather** in Telegram, then:\n\n1. Send `/mybots`\n2. Select your bot\n3. Click **Edit Bot** → **Edit Name**\n4. Type the new name\n\nThat changes how it appears in chats and the bot list. If you also want to change the bot username (the @handle), that's a separate option under **Edit Bot** → **Edit Username**.\n\nWhat are you renaming it to?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":629,"output":143,"cacheRead":110592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774678509090}}
