{"type":"message","id":"9fbec147","parentId":"88db3bdb","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:30:32.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All sites are blocking me. Without the Brave Search API key, I can't do proper web searches. Let me be honest with the user about this.\n\nActually, I don't know anything about \"Dhurandhar 2\" - it might be a real movie or it might be fictional. Without being able to search, I can't verify. Let me just be upfront.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Honestly, I can't pull up reviews right now — no search API key configured (we never set up Brave Search) and every review site is blocking the headless browser. 😅\n\nThat's another reason to get that Brave API key set up — I'd actually be useful for stuff like this instead of just shrugging.\n\nWhat did *you* think of it though? Give me your rating — I trust your taste more than some random IMDb score anyway. ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":588,"output":255,"cacheRead":113664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114507,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774700990030}}
