{"type":"message","id":"4a50695d","parentId":"2c7a6e75","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:31:04.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is checking if I'm here. The web search worked and I got results for Dhurandhar 2, but it seems like the message with the review results didn't get sent to the user (maybe because the gateway restarted or there was a delivery issue). Let me respond and share the review results.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Yes! Web search is working now — I actually pulled up the Dhurandhar 2 reviews right before you pinged. Here's the summary:\n\n**Dhurandhar: The Revenge** — Released March 19, 2026. Stars Ranveer Singh, Arjun Rampal, Sanjay Dutt, R. Madhavan. Directed by Aditya Dhar.\n\n**The good:**\n- Ranveer Singh is getting \"career best\" praise — Karan Johar called it his finest work\n- Times Now compared Aditya Dhar's two-parter achievement to Anurag Kashyap's Gangs of Wasseypur\n- Action, twists, and performances are getting love\n- Crossed ₹1,088 crore globally in first week — massive blockbuster\n\n**The mixed:**\n- Indian Express says it \"lacks the mazaa of the original\" and misses Akshaye Khanna's character\n- Hindustan Times found the nuance not as sharp as part 1\n- NewsLaundry called out the pro-establishment propaganda angle and weak antagonist\n\n**TL;DR:** Big crowd-pleaser, Ranveer carries it hard, but doesn't quite hit the magic of the first one. Sounds like you enjoyed it though — that's what matters! 🍿⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":201,"output":412,"cacheRead":123328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774711838425}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f7fd27c","parentId":"4a50695d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:32:15.326Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"149\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-28 15:32 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nhow much violence does it have"}],"timestamp":1774711935311}}
{"type":"message","id":"16efb01d","parentId":"3f7fd27c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:32:30.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the violence level in Dhurandhar 2. From the search results I already got, I know it received an A (adults only) certificate for strong violence. Let me search for more specific details.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_039b4eebeefb46309fa53e4b","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":3,"query":"Dhurandhar 2 violence level A certificate scenes graphic"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":516,"output":138,"cacheRead":123520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124174,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774711935323}}
{"type":"message","id":"e63e2462","parentId":"16efb01d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:32:36.425Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_039b4eebeefb46309fa53e4b","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Dhurandhar 2 violence level A certificate scenes graphic\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 5810,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"877edea806f031a8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n\\\"Dhurandhar 2\\\" has been granted an 'A' certificate by the Central Board of Film Certification (CBFC) in India and an 18 rating by the Irish Censor Board, signifying its content is suitable only for adult audiences due to a high level of violence and graphic scenes.\\n\\nThe film features brutal action sequences, strong violence, and explicit language. Reports indicate numerous graphic depictions, including:\\n*   A particularly brutal beheading where a severed head is also played with like a football, a scene reportedly based on a real-life incident.\\n*   Characters being shot in the face.\\n*   Scenes involving eyes being gouged or smashed.\\n*   Skulls being crushed with a hammer and a cement block.\\n*   Characters dying in explosions or being set on fire.\\n\\nWhile the CBFC mandated some modifications, including shortening visuals of extreme violence such as a 24-second cut in a beheading and kicking scene, and 2-4 second cuts for scenes of skulls being crushed and eyes being smashed, the film largely retains its intense and brutal nature. A disclaimer about disturbing content is also included, recommending strong viewer discretion. The film is described as delivering \\\"shocking brutality\\\" and \\\"sheer mayhem\\\" on screen.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"877edea806f031a8\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment-news/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-censor-certification-details-revealed-ranveer-singh-film-to-feature-strong-violence-and-report-article-153832450\",\n      \"title\": \"timesnownews.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://m.dailyhunt.in/news/india/english/odisha+bytes-epaper-obytes/dhurandhar+the+revenge+gets+18+certification+overseas+for+violence+explicit+content-newsid-n704553651\",\n      \"title\": \"dailyhunt.in\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.india.com/entertainment/dhurandhar-2-these-4-big-scenes-are-trimmed-by-cbfc-from-ranveer-singh-aditya-dhars-spy-thriller-8346694/\",\n      \"title\": \"india.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/cbfc-asks-dhurandhar-2-makers-to-trim-violence-correct-demonetisation-dates-ram-gopal-varma-calls-ranveer-singh-starrer-sholay-x-100-10587998/\",\n      \"title\": \"indianexpress.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/dhurandhar-the-revenge-censor-certification-details-revealed-ahead-of-release-ranveer-singh-starrer-to-feature-strong-violence/articleshow/129567924.cms\",\n      \"title\": \"indiatimes.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-rated-strong-violence-irish-censor-board-4-hour-runtime-ranveer-singh-aditya-dhar-101773484519370.html\",\n      \"title\": \"hindustantimes.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment-news/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-most-brutal-death-scenes-ranked-article-153878879\",\n      \"title\": \"timesnownews.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.zoomtventertainment.com/bollywood/dhurandhar-revenge-shocking-brutality-violent-moments-article-153879790\",\n      \"title\": \"zoomtventertainment.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/dhurandhar-2-full-list-of-cuts-edits-chopped-by-6-minutes-beheading-scene-censored-11230897\",\n      \"title\": \"ndtv.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/movies/dhurandhar-2-ranveer-singhs-spy-actioner-gets-a-certificate-with-21-modifications-as-it-crosses-rs-100-crore-in-pre-sales/article70756973.ece\",\n      \"title\": \"thehindu.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Dhurandhar 2 violence level A certificate scenes graphic","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":5810,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"877edea806f031a8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n\"Dhurandhar 2\" has been granted an 'A' certificate by the Central Board of Film Certification (CBFC) in India and an 18 rating by the Irish Censor Board, signifying its content is suitable only for adult audiences due to a high level of violence and graphic scenes.\n\nThe film features brutal action sequences, strong violence, and explicit language. Reports indicate numerous graphic depictions, including:\n*   A particularly brutal beheading where a severed head is also played with like a football, a scene reportedly based on a real-life incident.\n*   Characters being shot in the face.\n*   Scenes involving eyes being gouged or smashed.\n*   Skulls being crushed with a hammer and a cement block.\n*   Characters dying in explosions or being set on fire.\n\nWhile the CBFC mandated some modifications, including shortening visuals of extreme violence such as a 24-second cut in a beheading and kicking scene, and 2-4 second cuts for scenes of skulls being crushed and eyes being smashed, the film largely retains its intense and brutal nature. A disclaimer about disturbing content is also included, recommending strong viewer discretion. The film is described as delivering \"shocking brutality\" and \"sheer mayhem\" on screen.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"877edea806f031a8\">>>","citations":[{"url":"https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment-news/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-censor-certification-details-revealed-ranveer-singh-film-to-feature-strong-violence-and-report-article-153832450","title":"timesnownews.com"},{"url":"https://m.dailyhunt.in/news/india/english/odisha+bytes-epaper-obytes/dhurandhar+the+revenge+gets+18+certification+overseas+for+violence+explicit+content-newsid-n704553651","title":"dailyhunt.in"},{"url":"https://www.india.com/entertainment/dhurandhar-2-these-4-big-scenes-are-trimmed-by-cbfc-from-ranveer-singh-aditya-dhars-spy-thriller-8346694/","title":"india.com"},{"url":"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/cbfc-asks-dhurandhar-2-makers-to-trim-violence-correct-demonetisation-dates-ram-gopal-varma-calls-ranveer-singh-starrer-sholay-x-100-10587998/","title":"indianexpress.com"},{"url":"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/dhurandhar-the-revenge-censor-certification-details-revealed-ahead-of-release-ranveer-singh-starrer-to-feature-strong-violence/articleshow/129567924.cms","title":"indiatimes.com"},{"url":"https://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-rated-strong-violence-irish-censor-board-4-hour-runtime-ranveer-singh-aditya-dhar-101773484519370.html","title":"hindustantimes.com"},{"url":"https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment-news/bollywood/dhurandhar-2-most-brutal-death-scenes-ranked-article-153878879","title":"timesnownews.com"},{"url":"https://www.zoomtventertainment.com/bollywood/dhurandhar-revenge-shocking-brutality-violent-moments-article-153879790","title":"zoomtventertainment.com"},{"url":"https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/dhurandhar-2-full-list-of-cuts-edits-chopped-by-6-minutes-beheading-scene-censored-11230897","title":"ndtv.com"},{"url":"https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/movies/dhurandhar-2-ranveer-singhs-spy-actioner-gets-a-certificate-with-21-modifications-as-it-crosses-rs-100-crore-in-pre-sales/article70756973.ece","title":"thehindu.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774711956421}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a4830a0","parentId":"e63e2462","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:33:03.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Pretty intense violence. Let me give a clear summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Pretty brutal. Got an **A certificate** from CBFC and an **18 rating** in Ireland. Here's what's in it:\n\n- Beheading scene where a severed head gets kicked around like a football (based on a real incident)\n- People shot in the face\n- Eyes being gouged/smashed\n- Skulls crushed with hammers and cement blocks\n- Characters dying in explosions, set on fire\n\nCBFC actually made them cut stuff — trimmed a beheading scene by 24 seconds, cut 2-4 seconds from skull crushing and eye smashing scenes. Even after the cuts, it's described as \"shocking brutality\" and \"sheer mayhem.\"\n\nDefinitely not a casual family outing movie 😅 You went in prepared or was it a surprise?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1817,"output":185,"cacheRead":123520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125522,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774711956432}}
