 see what messages I sent in the group. The issue is that the bot was only responding when mentioned, so let me see if there are any sessions for the group chat that I can check.\\n\\nLet me look at the session history for the group chat.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Let me check what I actually said in the group.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_9713210822d6463ca8466119\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 10,\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"kilocode\",\n          \"model\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 526,\n            \"output\": 193,\n            \"totalTokens\": 141903,\n            \"cacheRead\": 141184,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774765867878\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:telegram:direct:7924461837","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","displayName":"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:7924461837","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1774765866458,"sessionId":"7cc27798-f9e7-4305-9061-606bbae0fb1d","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","contextTokens":1048576,"totalTokens":141220,"thinkingLevel":"high","systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:7924461837","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/7cc27798-f9e7-4305-9061-606bbae0fb1d.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue. The log shows `\"reason